CalculateAmountToTransferWithYield_Integration_Concrete_Test
├── given total wstETH zero
│  └── it should return zero
└── given total wstETH not zero
   ├── given total WETH zero
   │  └── it should return zero
   └── given total WETH not zero
      ├── when user WETH exceeds share balance
      │  ├── it should return the correct fee amount
      │  └── it should return the correct amount to transfer to user
      └── when user WETH not exceed share balance
         ├── it should return correct amount to transfer to user
         └── it should return zero fee amount
